sys_update_xml.name: sys_ws_operation_e7150c97db40734054d8ff621f96198f
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>POST</http_method><name>addAsset</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
	var data = request.body.data;
	var method = data.method.toString();
	var id = '';
	if(method == 'insert'){
		var model1 = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_model');
		    model1.initialize();
		    model1.cost = data.unit_cost.toString();
		    model1.description = data.description.toString();
		    model1.manufacture = data.manufacture.toString();
			model1.model_number = data.model_number.toString();
		    model1.name = data.name.toString();
			id = model1.insert();
		    id = checkAssets(id);
	}else if(method == 'update'){
		//model exist and update model
		var model2 = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_model');
		    model2.addQuery('model_number', data.model_number.toString());
		    model2.query();
		    model2.next();
			model2.cost = data.unit_cost.toString();
		    model2.description = data.description.toString();
		    model2.manufacture = data.manufacture.toString();
		    model2.name = data.name.toString();
		    id = model2.update();
		    id = checkAssets(id);
	}else if(method == 'check'){
		//check model exist
		var model = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_model');
		    model.addQuery('model_number', data.model_number.toString());
		    model.query();
		var count = model.getRowCount();
		if(count == 0){
			id = '0';
		}else{
			id = '1';
		}
	}
    
	return id;
	
	function checkAssets(model_id){
		var asset_id = '';
		//determine assets exist or not. If yes, update total. or insert a new record in assets table.
		var asset = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_etrack_assets');
		    asset.addQuery('model.sys_id', model_id);
		    asset.addQuery('stockroom.sys_id', data.stockroom);
		asset.query();
		var count1 = asset.getRowCount();
		if(count1 == 0){
			//add new asset
			asset_id = addAssets(model_id);
		}else{
			//assets exist, add amount to total of assets 
			asset_id = updateAssets(model_id);
		}
		
		return asset_id;
	}
	
	function addAssets(model_id){
		var asset1 = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_etrack_assets'); 
			asset1.initialize();
			asset1.barcode = data.barcode.toString();
			asset1.model = model_id;
		    asset1.owner = data.ownerId;
		    asset1.quantity = data.quantity;
			asset1.stockroom = data.stockroom;
			var asset_id = asset1.insert();
		return asset_id;
	}
	
	function updateAssets(model_id){
		var asset2 = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_etrack_assets');
			asset2.addQuery('model.sys_id', model_id);
		    asset2.addQuery('stockroom.sys_id', data.stockroom);
			asset2.query();
			asset2.next();
		    var quantity = asset2.quantity.toString();
			if(data.quatity === null || data.quantity.toString().trim().length == 0){
				data.quantity = "0";
			}
		    var quantityNum = parseInt(quantity) + parseInt(data.quantity.toString());
			asset2.quantity = quantityNum;
			asset2.barcode = data.barcode.toString();
			asset2.model = model_id;
		    asset2.owner = data.ownerId;
			asset2.stockroom = data.stockroom;
		    var asset_id = asset2.update();
		 return asset_id;
	}
	
})(request, response);

]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_naci_e_tracking/etrack_rest_api/addAsset</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/addAsset</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-12 17:33:23</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>e7150c97db40734054d8ff621f96198f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>36</sys_mod_count><sys_name>addAsset</sys_name><sys_package display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System" source="x_naci_e_tracking">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_e7150c97db40734054d8ff621f96198f</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-13 15:12:49</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="ETrack REST API">ac0dd2b6db00334054d8ff621f96192b</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>POST</http_method><name>transferAsset</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
	var data = request.body.data;
	
	var transfer = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_assdets_transfer');
	    transfer.initialize();
	    transfer.asset = data.assetId.toString();
	    transfer.current_user = data.assignToId.toString();
		transfer.comments = data.comments.toString();
		transfer.from = data.stockroomId.toString();
		transfer.quantity = data.quantity.toString();
		transfer.to = data.stockroomTo.toString();
		transfer.transfer_start_time = new GlideDateTime();
		transfer.insert();
	
	var asset = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_etrack_assets');
		asset.get(data.assetId.toString());
		asset.quantity = parseInt(asset.quantity.toString()) - parseInt(data.quantity.toString());
		var id = asset.update();
  
	return id;
})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_naci_e_tracking/etrack_rest_api/transferAsset</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/transferAsset</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-14 20:38:10</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>95a00bf7db00b30054d8ff621f961904</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>transferAsset</sys_name><sys_package display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System" source="x_naci_e_tracking">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_95a00bf7db00b30054d8ff621f961904</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-14 20:54:40</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="ETrack REST API">ac0dd2b6db00334054d8ff621f96192b</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>

	this.addStockroom = function(form){
			return $http({
				url: '/api/x_naci_e_tracking/etrack_rest_api/addStockRoom',
				method: 'POST',
				beforeSend: function(xhr){xhr.setRequestHeader('X-UserToken', window.g_ck);},
				headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json'},
				data: form
			})
		
	};
	
	this.checkStockroom = function(form){
		return $http({
				url: '/api/x_naci_e_tracking/etrack_rest_api/addStockRoom',
				method: 'POST',
				beforeSend: function(xhr){xhr.setRequestHeader('X-UserToken', window.g_ck);},
				headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json'},
				data: form
			})
		
	};
	
} ]]></script><sys_class_name>sp_angular_provider</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>abdullahz2@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-12 14:45:33</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>747e9bcfdb80f340b86770c08c9619f3</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_name>etrackingAddStockroom</sys_name><sys_package display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System" source="x_naci_e_tracking">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sp_angular_provider_747e9bcfdb80f340b86770c08c9619f3</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>abdullahz2@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-12 15:24:09</sys_updated_on><type>service</type></sp_angular_provider></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sp_theme"><sp_theme action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><css_variables>/** Service Portal */
$sp-tagline-color: #717171;
$sp-logo-margin-x: 1rem;
$sp-homepage-bg: #fff;
$sp-navbar-divider-color: #455464;

/** Media Query Breakpoints */
$screen-xs: 480px;
$screen-sm: 768px;
$screen-md: 992px;

/** Typography  */

/** Use Merriweather as the default serif font */

$font-size-base: 16px;

/** Colors */

$brand-info: #205493;

}

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ui_script"><sys_ui_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><description>Contains routes for etracking</description><global>false</global><name>x_naci_e_tracking.etrack-routes.js</name><script><![CDATA[(function(angular) {
	var app = angular.module('sn.$sp');
	app.requires.push('ui.router');

	// use hash-based routing
	app.config(function($locationProvider) {
		$locationProvider.html5Mode(false);
		$locationProvider.hashPrefix('!');
	});

	app.config(function($uiRouterProvider, $stateProvider) {
		// default to home state
		var $urlService = $uiRouterProvider.urlService;
		$urlService.rules.otherwise({ state: 'home' });		

		var states = [
			{
				name: 'home',
				url: '/home',
				component: 'spWidget',
				resolve: {
					widget: getWidget('etrack_home')
				},
			},

			{
				name: 'assets',
				url: '/assets',
				component: 'spWidget',
				resolve: {
					widget: getWidget('etrack_assets')
				}
			},

			{
				name: 'add_assets',
				url: '/add-assets',
				component: 'spWidget',
				resolve: {
					widget: getWidget('etrack_add_assets')
				},
			},

			{
				name: 'stockrooms',
				url: '/stockrooms',
				component: 'spWidget',
				resolve: {
					widget: getWidget('etrack_stockrooms')
				}
			},

			{
				name: 'add_stockrooms',
				url: '/add-stockrooms',
				component: 'spWidget',
				resolve: {
					widget: getWidget('etrack_add_stockroom')
				},
			},

			{
				name: 'report',
				url: '/report',
				component: 'spWidget',
				resolve: {
					widget: getWidget('etrack_report'),
				}
			},
			{
				name: 'display_stockroom',
				url: '/display-stockroom/:id',
				component: 'spWidget',
				resolve: {
					widget: function(spUtil, $stateParams) {
						return spUtil.get('etrack_display_stockroom', {
							id: $stateParams.id
						});
					}
				}
			},
			{
				name: 'display_asset',
				url: '/display-asset/:id',
				component: 'spWidget',
				resolve: {
					widget: function(spUtil, $stateParams) {
						return spUtil.get('etrack_asset_details', {
							id: $stateParams.id
						});
					}
				}
			},
			{
				name: 'edit_asset',
				url: '/edit-asset/:id',
				component: 'spWidget',
				resolve: {
					widget: function(spUtil, $stateParams) {
						return spUtil.get('etrack_edit_asset', {
							id: $stateParams.id
						});
					}
				}
			},
			{
				name: 'checkout_asset',

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ws_operation_e021fb3adb44334054d8ff621f961943
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>GET</http_method><name>fetchUserList</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
	 var users = [];
	 var searchCriteria = request.queryParams.term.toString();
	 var term = searchCriteria.split(" ");
	 var length = term.length;
	 var firstName = term[0];
	 var lastName = term.pop();
 
	 var user_item = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
	 var tmp = user_item.addQuery('first_name', 'STARTSWITH', firstName);
		 tmp.addOrCondition('u_preferred_firstname', 'STARTSWITH', firstName);
         if(length > 1) {
			 user_item.addQuery('last_name', 'STARTSWITH', lastName);
		 }
         user_item.query();
	 
	while(user_item.next()){
		 var value = user_item.getDisplayValue('first_name') + " " + user_item.getDisplayValue('last_name');
		 var label = value;
		 var id = user_item.getDisplayValue('sys_id');
		 var email = user_item.getDisplayValue('email');
		 var phone = user_item.getDisplayValue('phone');
		 var title = user_item.getDisplayValue('title');
		 var manager = user_item.getDisplayValue('manager');
		 var manager_id = user_item.manager.sys_id.toString();
		 var id_number = user_item.getDisplayValue('employee_number');
		 var institution = user_item.getDisplayValue("department");
		 var doc = user_item.getDisplayValue("u_long_org_division");
		 if (email) {
			 label += "  [" + email + "]";
		 }
		 users.push({label: label, value: value, id: id, email: email, phone: phone, title: title, id_number: id_number, manager: manager, manager_id: manager_id, institution: institution, doc: doc});
     }
   
     return users;
})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_naci_e_tracking/etrack_rest_api/fetchUserList</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/fetchUserList</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-11 21:24:36</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>e021fb3adb44334054d8ff621f961943</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>fetchUserList</sys_name><sys_package display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System" source="x_naci_e_tracking">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_e021fb3adb44334054d8ff621f961943</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-11 21:26:34</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="ETrack REST API">ac0dd2b6db00334054d8ff621f96192b</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ws_operation_ee3bdebbdb0c730054d8ff621f9619d5
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>POST</http_method><name>checkoutAsset</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
	var data = request.body.data;
	var id = '';
	
	var checkout = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_assets_check_out');
	    checkout.initialize();
	    checkout.asset = data.id.toString();
		checkout.quantity = parseInt(data.quantityCheckedout.toString());
	    checkout.comments = data.comments.toString();
	    checkout.current_user = data.checkOutUserID.toString();
	    checkout.checkout_time = new GlideDateTime();
		id = checkout.insert();
	
	var asset = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_etrack_assets');
	    asset.addQuery('sys_id', data.id.toString());
	    asset.query();
		asset.next();
	    asset.quantity = parseInt(asset.quantity.toString()) - parseInt(data.quantityCheckedout.toString());
	    id = asset.update();
	return id;

})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_naci_e_tracking/etrack_rest_api/checkoutAsset</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/checkoutAsset</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-14 17:56:39</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>ee3bdebbdb0c730054d8ff621f9619d5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_name>checkoutAsset</sys_name><sys_package display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System" source="x_naci_e_tracking">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_ee3bdebbdb0c730054d8ff621f9619d5</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-14 18:10:39</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="ETrack REST API">ac0dd2b6db00334054d8ff621f96192b</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>POST</http_method><name>updateAsset</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
	var data = request.body.data;
	
	var asset = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_etrack_assets');
	    asset.addQuery('sys_id', data.id.toString());
	asset.query();
	asset.next();
	asset.owner = data.ownerId.toString();
	asset.quantity = data.quantity.toString();
	asset.stockroom = data.stockroom.toString();
	asset.barcode = data.barcode.toString();
	var id = asset.update();
    
	return id;
})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_naci_e_tracking/etrack_rest_api/updateAsset</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/updateAsset</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-14 17:06:25</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>46b11ebbdbc8730054d8ff621f961979</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>updateAsset</sys_name><sys_package display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System" source="x_naci_e_tracking">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_46b11ebbdbc8730054d8ff621f961979</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-14 17:17:48</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="ETrack REST API">ac0dd2b6db00334054d8ff621f96192b</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ws_operation_e874fa7fdb8c730054d8ff621f961976
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>POST</http_method><name>checkinAsset</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
	var data = request.body.data;
	var asset_id = '';
	
    var checkout = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_assets_check_out');
	    checkout.get(data.id);
	    asset_id = checkout.asset.sys_id.toString();
	    checkout.checkin_by = data.user_id.toString();
	    checkout.checkin_time = new GlideDateTime();
	    checkout.update();
	
	var asset = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_etrack_assets');
	    asset.get(asset_id);
	    asset.quantity = parseInt(data.quantityCheckedOut.toString()) + parseInt(asset.quantity.toString());
	    var id = asset.update();
	
    return id;
})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_naci_e_tracking/etrack_rest_api/checkinAsset</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/checkinAsset</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-14 19:33:27</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>e874fa7fdb8c730054d8ff621f961976</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>checkinAsset</sys_name><sys_package display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System" source="x_naci_e_tracking">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_e874fa7fdb8c730054d8ff621f961976</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-14 19:48:40</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="ETrack REST API">ac0dd2b6db00334054d8ff621f96192b</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ws_operation_b10a4f33db40b30054d8ff621f961969
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>POST</http_method><name>completeTransfer</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
	var data = request.body.data;
	var quantity = '';
	var asset_id = '';
	
	var transfer = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_assdets_transfer');
	    transfer.get(data.id.toString());
	    quantity = transfer.quantity.toString();
	    asset_id = transfer.asset.sys_id.toString();
		transfer.receive_by = data.user_id.toString();
		transfer.transfer_complete_time = new GlideDateTime();
		transfer.update();
	
	var asset = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_etrack_assets');
	    asset.get(asset_id);
	    asset.quantity = parseInt(asset.quantity.toString()) + parseInt(quantity);
	    var id = asset.update();
    
	return id;
})(request, response);]]></operation_script><operation_uri>/api/x_naci_e_tracking/etrack_rest_api/completeTransfer</operation_uri><produces>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</produces><produces_customized>false</produces_customized><relative_path>/completeTransfer</relative_path><request_example/><requires_acl_authorization>true</requires_acl_authorization><requires_authentication>true</requires_authentication><short_description/><sys_class_name>sys_ws_operation</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2019-03-14 21:16:03</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>b10a4f33db40b30054d8ff621f961969</sys_id><sys_mod_count>1</sys_mod_count><sys_name>completeTransfer</sys_name><sys_package display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System" source="x_naci_e_tracking">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="NCI Equipment Tracking System">0d1eac28dbbfaf0054d8ff621f9619b2</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_ws_operation_b10a4f33db40b30054d8ff621f961969</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>zhoujim@nih.gov</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2019-03-14 21:32:26</sys_updated_on><web_service_definition display_value="ETrack REST API">ac0dd2b6db00334054d8ff621f96192b</web_service_definition><web_service_version/></sys_ws_operation></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_ws_operation_312007bedb80334054d8ff621f9619c8
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_ws_operation"><sys_ws_operation action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><consumes>application/json,application/xml,text/xml</consumes><consumes_customized>false</consumes_customized><default_operation_uri/><enforce_acl>cf9d01d3e73003009d6247e603f6a990</enforce_acl><http_method>POST</http_method><name>addStockRoom</name><operation_script><![CDATA[(function process(/*RESTAPIRequest*/ request, /*RESTAPIResponse*/ response) {
	var data = request.body.data;
	var id = '';
	if(data.method.toString() == 'insert'){
		var stockroom = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_stock_room');
			stockroom.initialize();
			stockroom.description = data.description.toString();
			stockroom.name = data.name.toString();
			stockroom.location = data.location.toString();
			stockroom.owner = data.ownerId.toString();
			stockroom.type = data.type.toString();
			id = stockroom.insert();
	}else if(data.method.toString() == 'update'){
		var stockroom1 = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_stock_room');
		    stockroom1.addQuery("name", data.name.toString());
			stockroom1.query();
		    stockroom1.next();
		   	stockroom1.description = data.description.toString();
			stockroom1.name = data.name.toString();
			stockroom1.location = data.location.toString();
			stockroom1.owner = data.ownerId.toString();
			stockroom1.type = data.type.toString();
		    id = stockroom1.update();
	}else if(data.method.toString() == 'check'){
		var stockroom2 = new GlideRecord('x_naci_e_tracking_stock_room');
		    stockroom2.addQuery("name", data.name.toString());
			stockroom2.query();
		    var count = stockroom2.getRowCount();
		if(count == 0){
			id = "0";
		}else{
			id = "1";
		}
	}
	
	return id;
